\subtree{
\title{Implementation Workflow}
\p{To add MCP integration to a plugin:}

\ol{
\li{Choose MCP server type (stdio, SSE, HTTP, ws)}
\li{Create \code{\startverb .mcp.json\stopverb} at plugin root with configuration}
\li{Use ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT} for all file references}
\li{Document required environment variables in README}
\li{Test locally with \code{\startverb /mcp\stopverb} command}
\li{Pre-allow MCP tools in relevant commands}
\li{Handle authentication (OAuth or tokens)}
\li{Test error cases (connection failures, auth errors)}
\li{Document MCP integration in plugin README}
}

\p{Focus on stdio for custom/local servers, SSE for hosted services with OAuth.}
}
}